"{\"uid\": \"si.com-college-virginia-uva-represented-with-14-olympians-on-team-usa-for-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The University of Virginia will be represented with 14 Olympians on Team USA at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States Olympic and Paralympic Committee finalized itsofficial Olympic rosterthis week and included among those nearly 600 American Olympians are a total of 14 athletes who compete, competed, or will compete at UVA or who graduated from UVA as non-athletes.\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9995152316856174, \"rank\": 0.0003957578649765798, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9772201056175142, \"rank\": 0.02329354553123387, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\", \"score\": 0.9999999548776951, \"rank\": 4.497728514666631e-08, \"text\": \"UVA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\", \"score\": 0.9999999548776951, \"rank\": 4.497728514666631e-08, \"text\": \"UVA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See the full list of UVA-affiliated athletes on the Team USA roster for the 2024 Paris Olympics below:Will Coleman - EquestrianDanielle Collins - TennisSkylar Dahl - Para-RowingKate Douglass - SwimmingThomas Heilman - Swimming (UVA swim & dive commit)Aaron Keith - Para-Cycling *UVA School of Medicine*Paige Madden - SwimmingEmma Navarro - Tennis *not a graduate*Matt Simpson - Goal Ball (Paralympics) *UVA Law*Emily Sonnett - SoccerAlex Walsh - SwimmingGretchen Walsh - Swimming (current undergrad)Emma Weber - Swimming (current undergrad)Bridget Williams - Track & Field  Included in that list are seven multi-time Olympians: Will Coleman (2012), Kate Douglass (2020), Aaron Keith (2020), Paige Madden (2020), Matt Simpson (2016 & 2020), Emily Sonnett (2020), and Alex Walsh (2020), six of whom are already Olympic medalists: Kate Douglass (bronze in 200m IM), Aaron Keith (silver in Para-Cycling), Paige Madden (silver in 4x200m free relay), Matt Simpson (silver in Goal Ball), Emily Sonnett (bronze in women's soccer), and Alex Walsh (silver in 200m IM).\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6069049788455638, \"rank\": 0.6476159030168683, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Simpson_(poet)\", \"score\": 0.7026991944716803, \"rank\": 0.30769230769228495, \"text\": \"Matt Simpson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Simpson_(poet)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Simpson_(po